pageContext.claim: “They don't care so much about people pouring across the border -- MS-13. They're not worried about MS13, if anything they want to protect MS-13.”
pageContext.analysis: There's no evidence that Democrats want to "protect" the notorious Latin American gang known as MS-13. U.S. agencies have been dealing with enforcement and prevention of MS-13 activities since as early as 2004, including under the Obama administration.
